  "title": "Service Coordinator (3 months contract) up to $3300",
  "description": "<p></p><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Coordinate service schedules by liaising with service contractors and customers to arrange appointments.</li><li>Respond promptly and professionally to customer enquiries across multiple channels, including phone, email, live chat, WhatsApp, and walk-in interactions.</li><li>Compile, analyze, and prepare reports for management review.</li><li>Carry out additional duties and responsibilities as assigned by the Service Manager.</li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li>Diploma in Business Administration or a related field.</li><li>At least 3 years of relevant experience in after-sales or customer service roles.</li><li>Strong analytical, organizational, and documentation skills.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel.</li><li>Able to work independently and communicate effectively with both internal teams and external stakeholders.</li></ul><p>EA Personnel: Lou Kay Shaun Neal</p><p>EA Personnel No: R22109163</p><p>EA License No: 90C3026</p>",
