    "description": "<p>JAC is an international recruitment consultancy with over 45 years of specialised recruitment experience across Asia and Europe. We have over 1,200 expert consultants who have a deep cultural understanding of the local markets they operate in. Combined with our regional network and specialised industry focus we are renowned for placing highly skilled permanent and contracting staff into specialist positions.</p>\n<p>In Singapore, we cover the Banking and Financial Services, Corporate Services, Digital and Information Technology, Healthcare and Life Sciences, Industrial, Sales &amp; Marketing sectors. We also recruit for contract roles and have a dedicated team that can assist with hiring for Japanese-language skills.</p>\n<p>Our job board is updated daily so you can stay updated on jobs as they become available and find the next best role for you.</p>\n<p>EA License number: 90C3026</p>",
